      <tr>
        <td>Each game missed (depending on squad status) will boost a player's Squad DNA Rating by a PERCENTAGE of their already calculated Squad DNA Rating.</td>
        <td>Every 5% below 100% Match Sharpness (depending on squad status) will boost a player's Squad DNA Rating by a PERCENTAGE of their already calculated Squad DNA Rating.</td>
        <td>Overall Risk will be added to a player's current condition before multiplying by their Squad DNA Rating to give the final Matchday Rating</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>[Default: 0, will have no effect on Matchday Rating]<br>A Key Player with a Squad DNA Rating of 100, with a Games Missed Handicap of 10, who has missed 2 games will then have an updated Squad DNA Rating of 120. Recommended values: 0 - 25</td>
        <td>[Default: 0, will have no effect on Matchday Rating]<br>A Key Player with a Squad DNA Rating of 100, with a Match Sharpness Handicap of 15, who has a current Match Sharpness rating of 88% will then have an updated Squad DNA Rating of 130. Recommended values: 0 - 15</td>
